      "description": "$4,800 - Older car in poor overall condition and being sold honestly as a project, fixer-upper, or possible parts car. Expect significant cosmetic wear throughout, including faded or tired paint, visible blemishes, and a generally worn appearance inside and out. It will likely need mechanical attention and deferred maintenance, so buyers should not expect a turn-key daily driver. Best suited for someone looking for an inexpensive project, a budget repair candidate, or a parts vehicle.",
