    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Needs work and is being sold as an honest poor-condition vehicle. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear throughout, including exterior blemishes, paint and trim aging, and a worn interior that shows heavy use. It is not a clean, turnkey example, and buyers should plan on deferred maintenance and possible repairs to bring it up to a more dependable standard. Best suited for someone looking for a budget buy, a project, or basic transportation with realistic expectations.",
