    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly car that offers dependable basic transportation and strong value for the money. This vehicle shows its age and wear, but it starts, runs, and gives the next owner an affordable way to get on the road without a big upfront cost. An excellent choice for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone looking for inexpensive wheels at a realistic price.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runner with real potential for someone who wants affordable transport, a handy backup vehicle, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s priced to reflect its age and condition, and if you\u2019re the kind of buyer who appreciates straightforward deals and good value, this could be a great fit. Come have a look and see if it\u2019s the right one for you.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project car with good bones and plenty of upside for the right buyer. The powertrain fires up and the chassis feels like a solid foundation, making this a great candidate for a budget build, daily-driver revival, or parts donor. Shows cosmetic wear and needs attention as expected, but it has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout enthusiasts appreciate. If you know your way around a toolbox, there\u2019s real value here.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Used and rough, priced to move. Clean title. Come get it.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with real presence\u2014an honest, road-worn machine that still carries a certain charm every time you walk up to it. It\u2019s the kind of vehicle that appeals to someone who sees possibility: a dependable around-town runabout, a practical spare, or the perfect canvas for a hands-on project. It has the seasoned character and lived-in personality that newer cars just can\u2019t fake, and for the right buyer it offers a budget-friendly way into ownership with plenty of potential to make it your own.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
