      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at a budget-friendly price. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer seeking practical value, a starter vehicle, or a project opportunity. A sensible way to get on the road without overspending.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
